Package: BCGLMs
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Compostional GLMs for Analyzing Microbiome Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Li Zhang
Maintainer: Li Zhang <lzhang28@uab.edu>
Description: Functions for fitting Bayesian compositional generalized linear models for analyzing microbiome data (BCGLM) with structured regularized horseshoe prior and a soft sum-to-zero restriction on coefficients through the prior distribution. 
Depends: brms,BhGLM,phyloseq,stats,MASS
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
